channel.title: I Think I'm Ip Banned, Please Help Me! :\
channel.description:
[img]http://puu.sh/J5D1[/img]
Now i'm a very active member since i began at this community, i'm learning how to code java and tbh this is like the best place to learn everything i need to about Rsps, rune-server & runelocus don't really help out much and aren't active like this rsps community, so if someone will please un ip ban me or help me out i would really appreciate it.
My account isn't banned because i just logged in it thru my Vps, i guess im just ipbanned? Well hopefully i can get some help.
If you read this keep bumping it up until a moderator or administrator reads please.
Thank you for reading.

item.title: I Think I'm Ip Banned, Please Help Me! :\
item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

Try reseting your router to fetch yourself a new IP. I checked around and it doesn’t seem you were directly banned for doing anything, so you must’ve gotten unlucky and was given an IP that was banned for something else.

I’ll close this now, but message me if you need any more help.
